"#feedbackModal_main_2529800\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lzo1665702733691.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lzo1665702733691.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lzo1665702733691.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lzo1665702733691\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                       \n Oracle Installation and Configuration Considerations\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__oracle_installation_and_configuration_considerations_163875\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__topic_d36432e1_d36433e1_d36434e1_d36435e1_d36436e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173320e52\">\n            Requirements\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55109e1_d55110e1_d55111e1\">You must install the Pro*C/C++ precompiler before you can use Uniface with Oracle. In particular, you should make sure that the following are present:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25391e1_d25392e1_d25393e1\">The Pro*C/C++ libraries to which Uniface links.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25394e1_d25395e1_d25396e1\">The link utility or link description files for the operating system (for example, makefiles on Unix). The Uniface installation program analyzes these files to determine the link information it needs.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55112e1_d55113e1_d55114e1\">User-defined 3GL can use both the precompiler interface and the Oracle Call Interface (OCI).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__topic_d36437e1_d36438e1_d36439e1_d36440e1_d36441e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173320e75\">\n            Supported Oracle Products\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55118e1_d55119e1_d55120e1\">Uniface supports the Oracle RDBMS, as well as the database options shown in the following table:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Oracle Options Supported by Uniface</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Oracle Product</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Required</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Recommended</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Procedural Option</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Distributed Option</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parallel Server</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lzo1665702733691__table_d5087e1_d5088e1_d5089e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55121e1_d55122e1_d55123e1\">Uniface has the following extra functionality when it is connected to an Oracle server with the Procedural Option:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25397e1_d25398e1_d25399e1\">Uniface creates and uses stored packages which improve performance.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25400e1_d25401e1_d25402e1\">PL/SQL (including stored procedure calls) can be used in the SQL Workbench and in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">sql</code> ProcScript statement.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55124e1_d55125e1_d55126e1\">The functionality enabled by the Distributed Option and Parallel Server is transparent to Uniface.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55127e1_d55128e1_d55129e1\">SQL*Net is supported by Uniface.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__topic_d36442e1_d36443e1_d36444e1_d36445e1_d36446e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1173320e240\">\n                        \n Unsupported Products\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__p_d55133e1_d55134e1_d55135e1\">The following Oracle products are not supported by Uniface:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25403e1_d25404e1_d25405e1\">SQL*Module 3GL\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25406e1_d25407e1_d25408e1\">SQL*Connect\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lzo1665702733691__li_d25409e1_d25410e1_d25411e1\">Trusted Oracle\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529800\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529800\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Oracle Installation and Configuration Considerations Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Oracle Installation and Configuration Considerations Requirements You must install the Pro*C/C++ precompiler before you can use Uniface with Oracle. In particular, you should make sure that the following are present: The Pro*C/C++ libraries to which Uniface links. The link utility or link description files for the operating system (for example, makefiles on Unix). The Uniface installation program analyzes these files to determine the link information it needs. User-defined 3GL can use both the precompiler interface and the Oracle Call Interface (OCI). Supported Oracle Products Uniface supports the Oracle RDBMS, as well as the database options shown in the following table: Table 1. Oracle Options Supported by Uniface Oracle Product Required Supported Recommended Procedural Option No Yes Yes Distributed Option No Yes No Parallel Server No Yes No Uniface has the following extra functionality when it is connected to an Oracle server with the Procedural Option: Uniface creates and uses stored packages which improve performance. PL/SQL (including stored procedure calls) can be used in the SQL Workbench and in the sql ProcScript statement. The functionality enabled by the Distributed Option and Parallel Server is transparent to Uniface. SQL*Net is supported by Uniface. Unsupported Products The following Oracle products are not supported by Uniface: SQL*Module 3GL SQL*Connect Trusted Oracle Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}